Premium/House Tutors Assignments
Ways to apply for an assignment:

1. Apply via the provided link @ https://www.premiumtutors.sg/assignmentapplication

2. Email us at contact@premiumtutors.sg or message the coordinator directly with the following info:

Assignment Code:
Name:
Age, Gender, Race:
Address:
Contact Number:
Qualifications:
Current Occupation:
Relevant Results:
Tuition Experience (in years):
Brief description of experience in relevant subject(s):
Preferred timings:
Expected hourly rate:

Furthermore, a referral fee of 30% of our commission will be given to any tutor who refers to us any available tuition assignments which we are able to match.

Message @bryanPT if you have any enquiries or referrals
